room_title: Escape room "Trapped in Space" by The Escape Artist in Seattle
review: Oh what fun! Friends and did the Lost in Space room at The Escape Artist today and I have to say it was super fun! It complicated and exciting and oh gee, we barely made it out but at the last minute we did! Whew!
